snippet.title: Empires Apart - Announcement Trailer (Pre-Alpha Footage)
snippet.description:
Empires Apart is an old-school medieval RTS for PC/Mac developed by DESTINYbit.

Gather resources, raise an army and lead your civilization to victory!

(Pre-Alpha Footage)

Follow development at http://empiresapart.net
Forums http://empiresapart.net/forums
Twitter http://twitter.com/empiresapart
Facebook http://facebook.com/empiresapart
